; Regression test for issue #798: ledger xml/json doesn't report all xacts (BZ#798)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/798
; Verify that xml command reports all transactions in the journal

2015/01/01 First
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

2015/01/15 Second
    Expenses:Dining  $25.00
    Assets:Cash

2015/02/01 Third
    Expenses:Rent    $500.00
    Assets:Checking

